  <brief_title>The Efficacy and Safety of Curcuma Domestica Extracts and Ibuprofen in Knee Osteoarthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Efficacy and Safety of Curcuma Domestica Extracts and Ibuprofen for Therapy of Patients With Knee Osteoarthritis, the Randomized Double-blinded Controlled Trial, Multicenter Study</official_title>
